ygData.subject: Where to fight??
ygData.msgSnippet: I am a Lvl 10 SK and I haven t played him for a while cause i can t find a good place to fight.  I either die a lot or get barely any exp.  I do like to group
ygData.messageBody:
I am a Lvl 10 SK and I haven't played him for a while cause i can't find a
good place to fight. I either die a lot or get barely any exp. I do like to
group but I seem to only get one for like 1/2 at a time and it is hard to find
a group for such a short time and I hate leaving people in tough areas when I
leave. Any help would be great. I don't mind traveling either so any
suggestions will help.

Thanks

Sanil
Lvl 10 SK

A proud member of the SK brotherhood!
